title: Pop.Art.Studio.v2.2.Portable.rar
description:
WEBSITE: http://www.fotoview.nl/

Create your own Pop Art masterpieces in the famous Andy Warhol and Roy Lichtenstein Style.

Pop Art Studio is very easy to use graphics editing software. It supports BMP, JPG, GIF, PNG and TIFF formatted images.
Version 2.2 contains many Andy Warhol effects and the famous Roy Lichtenstein effect. It provides an endless selection of text and drawing tools, filters, gradients and color adjustment capabilities. This version also supports layered images. The Template Library provides many useful examples of layered designs.

Effects include Paul Klee, Piet Mondriaan, picture frames, flags, psychedelic, color accent, texture, unsharp mask, slide show and many more...
